```
── shipping-rate-service_b1_gradual_rep1 ──
  🟢 INFO:     k6 dropped 5840 iterations (expected for under-provisioned baseline)
  🟢 INFO:     Error rate 46.00% (expected for under-provisioned baseline)
  🟡 WARNING:  1 Prometheus scrape gap >30s
  🔴 CRITICAL: Pods not healthy at export: shipping-rate-service=CrashLoopBackOff
  🟢 INFO:     Observed 5 pod restarts (expected under baseline overload)

  Critical issues: 1
  Warnings:        1
```

The validator correctly flags a **critical issue**. But the real story goes much deeper.

